{"id":351750,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jan_Decleir","text":"Jan Decleir (born 14 February 1946) is a Belgian movie and stage actor. He was born in Niel, Antwerp.\nHis first big role was in Fons Rademakers' \"Mira\" (1971). He starred in Academy Award winning movies \"Karakter\" and \"Antonia\" and the Oscar-nominated social drama \"Daens\".\nFor his role in \"The Barons\", he received the Magritte Award for Best Supporting Actor.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Belgians","surface_form":"Belgian","offset":41},{"uri":"Movie_actor","surface_form":"movie","offset":49},{"uri":"Actor","surface_form":"actor","offset":65},{"uri":"Niel","surface_form":"Niel","offset":87},{"uri":"Antwerp_(province)","surface_form":"Antwerp","offset":93},{"uri":"Fons_Rademakers","surface_form":"Fons Rademakers","offset":128},{"uri":"Mira_(film)","surface_form":"Mira","offset":146},{"uri":"Academy_Awards","surface_form":"Academy Award","offset":174},{"uri":"Character_(1997_film)","surface_form":"Karakter","offset":204},{"uri":"Antonia%27s_Line","surface_form":"Antonia","offset":219},{"uri":"Daens_(film)","surface_form":"Daens","offset":266},{"uri":"Magritte_Award","surface_form":"Magritte Award","offset":320}]}